# Mini Backend Project

# Project Overview
This project demonstrates a full backend application using **Python Flask** and **SQLite**. The application allows users to register, login, and manage student records through a dashboard with CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations.  

# Features
- User registration  
- User login (basic authentication)  
- Dashboard displaying student records  
- Add new student record  
- Edit existing record  
- Delete record from database  
- Data stored using SQLite database  

# Project Structure
Week4_Backend_Project/  
- app.py  
- database.db  
- templates/  
  - index.html        # Homepage / Dashboard  
  - register.html     # Registration page  
  - login.html        # Login page  
  - dashboard.html    # Dashboard with student CRUD  
  - edit_student.html # Edit student page  
- README.md  

# Technologies Used
- Python  
- Flask  
- SQLite  
- HTML  

# How to Run the Project
1. Open the project folder in VS Code.  
2. Install Flask if not installed:  
   ```bash
   pip install flask